The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Vishy award
                                                     Vishy award
            A STAFF REPORTER            Viswanath                           
	Calcutta: Former India captain Gundappa Viswanath will receive the Castrol Lifetime Achievement in Cricket Award this year, while all-rounder Ravindra Jadeja will get the Junior Cricketer of the Year Award for 2008.         
	Viswanath would receive Rs 5 lakh and a trophy at the awards function in Mumbai on Thursday, a release said.                                                                                                                       
